title: Richard Krasnesky
text: Whether by phone or email, the professionals at Doheny's meet my expectations everytime. I have actually stopped shopping for deals on pool supplies, I just order what I need and trust that Doheny's is competitive on price and quality. Got 30 minutes a season back and I can't say how important that is to me
